## Next Recommended Order

1. Run `Governance Validation Recovery Sprint` to clear MockDB/unit timeout and generated artifact policy.
2. Run `AxodusAPP Test Stabilization Sprint` to restore frontend test reliability.
3. Run `Trading Local E2E Environment Sprint` with no live trading or provider execution.
