7. Define validation gates for `Business`, `ACS`, `Lottery`, `BBA-Agency`, and `Documentation`.

## Risk Preservation Rules

Do not modify:

- Trading nested repos
- DEX nested repos
- credential paths
- vendor forks
- token-list repos
- generated artifacts
- Core runtime/adapters/release tags

Do not enable:

- runtime execution
- settlement
- production configuration
- live trading
- paper trading
- real adapters
- treasury or chain execution
